                <th scope="row">\( \overrightarrow{V}=\left\| \overrightarrow{V} \right\|\;\;\overrightarrow{\mu_V}\;\text{ con}\;\;\overrightarrow{\mu_V}=\frac{\overrightarrow{V}}{\left\| \overrightarrow{V} \right\|} \)</th>
              </tr>
